OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and overcast morning
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of showery rain
OL,7,Fspreading southeastwards. A drier
OL,8,Fafternoon with some brighter spells,
OL,9,Fbut still a few showers possible,
OL,10,Fthese heavy at times in the west.
OL,11,FDrier in the east later. Feeling
OL,12,Frather cool.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy and dry
OL,15,Fevening but with the odd isolated
OL,16,Fshower possible. Becoming dry
OL,17,Fovernight with clear intervals
OL,18,Fdeveloping near northern coasts.
OL,19,FMostly light easterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
